@startuml activity_diagram
title Activity Diagram with Swimlanes - Parking Reservation and Payment Flow

|Driver/User|
start
:Open mobile app / kiosk;
:Request available parking spaces;

|Parking Management System|
:Receive availability request;
:Request live occupancy data;

|Sensor/Camera System|
:Send occupancy and entry/exit data;

|Parking Management System|
:Validate live data;
:Read parking records;
:Calculate available spaces;

if (Parking space available?) then (Yes)
  :Display available spaces;

  |Driver/User|
  :Select parking space;

  |Parking Management System|
  :Check selected space availability;
  :Save reservation;
  :Create parking session;
  :Generate route guidance;
  :Display reservation and route;

  |Driver/User|
  :Park vehicle;
  :Request checkout;

  |Parking Management System|
  :Calculate parking fee;
  :Send payment request;

  |Payment Gateway|
  :Process payment;
  :Return payment result;

  |Parking Management System|
  if (Payment approved?) then (Yes)
    :Store payment transaction;
    :Mark session completed;
    :Display payment confirmation;
  else (No)
    :Display payment failure;
  endif
else (No)
  :Display "Parking Full";
endif

|Driver/User|
stop
@enduml
